posts.name: Drew B.
posts.cooked:
There’s been a huge amount of discussion about GrabCAD Workbench shutting down on June 1st and we’ve received a lot of questions here at Onshape about whether it will be a suitable replacement. Onshape can replace Workbench + your CAD software of choice with one unified tool.

To help your team make the decision and transition, the PTC Education team will be hosting a webinar today on Tuesday, May 23rd at 4PM (ET). We’ll discuss how you can set your team up, import your models, and get up to speed with Onshape. If you’re interested, you can sign up with the link below. If you’re unable to attend, signing up will ensure you’re sent a video of the recording.

Webinar Registration Link

Thanks all!

There were some good discussions between FRC teams and Onshape leadership at LiveWorx about ways to make part libraries and COTS parts usage easier, so a lot of key leaders know this is an area to keep improving on.
